             was indicted for <rs id="t18220417-209-off1099" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220417-209-off1099" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-209-off1099" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220417-209-cd1100" type="crimeDate">15th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-209-off1099 t18220417-209-cd1100"></join>, 236 lbs. of lead, value 2 l., belonging to 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-209-victim1904" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Hawes
                        <interp inst="t18220417-209-victim1904" type="surname" value="Hawes"></interp>
